    • Field Detail

      • attributes

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.List<java.lang.String>> attributes
        List of strings that describes the Noun that is divided according to the assertion of the Noun to the string, having their assertions as the key (e.g. CapableOf, HasProperty).

        The strings are not nouns.

      • id

        protected java.lang.String id
        The surface text of the noun

      • isCommon

        protected boolean isCommon
        Set to know if the Noun is a common noun or a proper noun. True for common, false for proper.

      • references

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,Noun>> references
        Map of nouns that has a assertion to the Noun that is divided according to the assertion of the Noun(class) to the nouns(map), having their assertion as the key (e.g. IsA, HasA, AtLocation).

        protected Noun.TypeOfNoun type
        The type of noun
